This is a simple and interesting project that allows you to use web scraping to extract product information from the eBay website and display 
it in a Streamlit application. In this project, you extract the product name, product price, and product image link from eBay, 
and then display them in a simple and user-friendly interface in Streamlit. This allows you to easily browse and analyze product information,
as well as gain practical experience in web scraping and building web applications.
